page.title: 15HOME LIFE III
page.content: At weekends I normally wake up when I feel like it.On Saturdays I get up very early because I normally go out shopping with my mate. We go shopping because we like going in shops and looking at different clothes and trying them on,I also like spending my money. After that we normally go into Olivers for a bite to eat. It's very posh in there ,their food is quite healthy because of their salad and stuff. After all that we carry on looking around and around.Sometimes I think there should be more things to do.
